{"name":"Happyshop","permalink":"happyshop","crunchbase_url":"http://www.crunchbase.com/company/happyshop","homepage_url":"http://www.happyshop.com","blog_url":"http://blog.happyshop.com/","blog_feed_url":"","twitter_username":"","category_code":"mobile","number_of_employees":60,"founded_year":2010,"founded_month":11,"founded_day":null,"deadpooled_year":null,"deadpooled_month":null,"deadpooled_day":null,"deadpooled_url":null,"tag_list":"mobile, latam, retail, mobile-marketing, chile, qr, barcodes, shopping, app, mobile-app, ebay, foursquare, livingsocial, groupon, deals, offers, located-based, lbs, gmlc, mobile-commerce, mcommerce, marketing, ecommerce, check-in, sca","alias_list":null,"email_address":"","phone_number":"56991620004","description":"Mobile Media  Platform","created_at":"Thu Sep 01 19:27:44 UTC 2011","updated_at":"Wed Oct 24 02:34:10 UTC 2012","overview":"<p>We are convinced that mobile can push a change in consumer behavior never seen before, bridging online and offline into a single delightful experience.</p>\n\n<p>Mobile rapidly changes both consumers’ expectations and the overall shopping experience, that´s why Happyshop born….</p>\n\n<p>Happyshop is the first technology platform (core in mobile) that can give the highest relevance (&amp; conversion) for mutichannel advertising. </p>\n\n<p>Our mision is to enhance the shopping experience and improve comunication to prepare retail and brands to the new shopper 2.0 and the Onmichannel world.</p>\n\n<p>We drive happyshopppers! Because we give them only the content and offers they value in the best moment, place and real time!\nWe are very exciting about integrating online and offline media channels!</p>\n\n<p>Currently Happyshop is working with some of the leadest retail companies in Latam (Falabella, Cencosud, Sodimac, Salcobrand, Parque Arauco) and important CPG brands (Loreal, Nivea, Nestle Eucerine, 3M..) </p>\n\n<p>HappyShop was the recipient of Innova Chile&#8217;s price and has also earned a government sponsored grant, allowing the start-up to attract the interest of various early stage investors and recently received more than 5,6 US$ MM in series A &amp; B funding. </p>\n\n<p>For brands, Happyshop has created a new and innovative mobile advertising format named “adinstore™”.</p>\n\n<p>With Happyshop Adinstore™ the brands can communicate in a personal way with the consumer during their “purchase decision process”, creating brand experiences that capture and engage customers and prospects from our advertisers. </p>\n\n<p>The main benefits of this new format is that we don&#8217;t break the mobile user experience and the great results in engagement (CTR higher 9%)  and performance for advertisers.</p>\n\n<p>You can see more information and videos:</p>\n\n<p>http://www.happyshop.com\nhttp://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0a0qyWb7dpI\nhttp://www.linkedin.com/company/happyshop</p>","image":{"available_sizes":[[[150,50],"assets/images/resized/0015/3562/153562v2-max-150x150.png"],[[250,83],"assets/images/resized/0015/3562/153562v2-max-250x250.png"],[[450,150],"assets/images/resized/0015/3562/153562v2-max-450x450.png"]],"attribution":null},"products":[],"relationships":[{"is_past":false,"title":"Co-Founder & President","person":{"first_name":"MarÃ­a","last_name":"Paz Gillet","permalink":"mara-paz-gillet","image":{"available_sizes":[[[150,150],"assets/images/resized/0016/3629/163629v2-max-150x150.jpg"],[[200,200],"assets/images/resized/0016/3629/163629v2-max-250x250.jpg"],[[200,200],"assets/images/resized/0016/3629/163629v2-max-450x450.jpg"]],"attribution":""}}},{"is_past":false,"title":"Chief Product Officer (CPO)","person":{"first_name":"Fabrizzio","last_name":"Andrioli","permalink":"fabrizzio-andrioli","image":null}},{"is_past":false,"title":"Co-Founder & Vicepresident","person":{"first_name":"AndrÃ©s","last_name":"Silva","permalink":"andrs-silva","image":null}},{"is_past":false,"title":"Board of Directors","person":{"first_name":"Raimundo","last_name":"Cerda","perma